premise_source_doc_sentence: After serving with the United States Army during World War II , Gray played baseball professionally from 1946 to 1950 for the Fulton Bulldogs  (  1946  )  , Fulton Chicks  (  1947  )  , Aberdeen Pheasants  (  1948  )  , Springfield Browns  (  1949  )  and Gloversville-Johnstown Glovers  (  1950  )  .
